title: Title 42 border policy for expelling immigrants upheld by federal court in DC - Fox News
content:
1. Title 42 border policy for expelling immigrants upheld by federal court in DC  Fox News

  4. U.S. can't exempt migrant children from border deportation policy, judge rules  CBS News

description: The U.S. government can continue to expel migrant families at the southern border under a public health policy known as Title 42, denying them a chance to ask for asylum, but can’t send them back to countries where their life or freedom will be in danger, a federal appeals court ruled Friday.
